AI Content Detection & Fact Checking with Genaios
 
At Genaios, our mission is to empower people to use the power of tech to safeguard the basis of all liberal democracies: trusted information. Our plugin offers powerful features like AI content detection and fact-checking scanning to validate the integrity of the information you access online.
 
Key Features:
 
✨AI Content Detection: Automatically identifies AI-generated content.
 
✨Fact Checking Scanning: Verifies the accuracy of the information you encounter.
 
Please note: Our model currently detects textbased content in English, German and Spanish.
 
Join us in our mission! Download now and let us know what you think.
